						               													<description>The Board Game Inspired By Nikola Tesla.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Tesla Science Race is an educational tabletop board game that teaches players about Nikola Tesla&amp;rsquo;s inventions and his life&amp;rsquo;s journey one dice roll at a time.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game can be played two ways - with a smart device or without. Special cards with QR codes were created to be used with smart devices in addition to the standard cards. The cards with the QR code include a link to the next task.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Players compete to collect as many of Tesla's inventions as possible. The inventions come in the form of a card, and on the back of each is one piece of Tesla&amp;rsquo;s infamous coil. This was one of his most significant inventions. Each player attempts to recreate the Tesla coil by assembling the cards like pieces of a puzzle. The player who first puts together the coil is the winner.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game is interactive, and educational as each player tests their knowledge of Tesla&amp;rsquo;s many inventions. The game also challenges players to think on the spot, as they make strategic decisions to not only move forward but to collect valuable invention cards.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;-description from publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
